! Morphological Transducer for Yiddish

Multichar_Symbols

! Part of speech categories
%<n%>    ! Noun
%<v%>    ! Verb
%<det%>  ! determiner
%<prn%>  ! pronoun

! number: for nouns, verbs, adjectives, determiners, etc.
%<pl%>   ! Plural
%<sg%>   ! Singular

! gender: for nouns, determiners, adjectives, etc.
%<m%>    ! masculine
%<f%>    ! feminine
%<nt%>   ! neuter

! person
%<p1%>
%<p2%>
%<p3%>

! cases: for determiners, etc.
%<nom%>  ! nominative
%<acc%>  ! accusative
%<dat%>  ! dative

! verb forms
%<inf%>  ! infinitive
%<pres%> ! present
%<pp%>   ! past participle
%<pprs%> ! present participle
%<imp%>  ! imperative

! Escaped characters

%{ь%}    ! used for umlaut of ~previous vowel
%>       ! morpheme boundary
%{ױ%}    ! for ױ to ײ umlaut correspondence

! matched features
%[%+pp%] ! past participle
%[%-pp%] ! past participle

! Regular umlaut correspondences:
! ו - י
! אָ - ע
! ױ - ײ/ײַ
! אַ - ע
אַ
אָ
ײַ
יִ
וּ
בּ
בֿ
כּ
כֿ
ךֿ
פֿ
פּ

