!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

LEXICON NounRoot

הױז:הױז N-N-UML-ER ; ! "house" plural with ײַ
בּױם:בּ%{ױ%}ם N-M-UML-ER ; ! "tree" plural with ײ
אַרבעט:אַרבעט N-F-S ; ! "work"
בּאַרג:בּאַרג N-M-UML ; ! "mountain"

LEXICON DetRoot

דער: DET-DEF-M ; ! "the"
די: DET-DEF-F ; ! "the"
דאָס: DET-DEF-N ; ! "the"
די: DET-DEF-PL ; ! "the"

LEXICON VerbRoot
%[%-pp%]:גע VerbStems ; ! past participle
VerbStems ; ! other forms


LEXICON VerbStems

קױפֿן:קױפֿ V-REG ;
פֿאַרלירן:פֿאַרליר V-REG-NOPREF ;
בּעטן:בּעט V-STRONG-7 ;

